Liquid Intelligent Technologies is a leading connectivity, innovation, and intelligent technology company that operates in 13 countries across Southern, Eastern, and Central Africa. It is committed to building a digital future for Africa through an approach that prioritises innovation and product development so that its solutions are always enduringly adaptable. Liquid Intelligent Technologies’ flexible and dynamic business model keeps it at the forefront of telecoms innovation, while its commitment to listening to its customers ensures that Liquid Intelligent Technologies’ solutions are constantly evolving to meet these customers’ needs. The company has benefited from the increased focus on digital transformation in recent years as its products and services perfectly suit the modern business. As these businesses continue to transform to meet the evolving needs of the workplace, Liquid Intelligent Technologies looks forward to supporting these organisations with its innovative products and services.